<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>Notification that a window is about to be closed by the windowing system (e.g. the user clicked the title bar close button). The <db:link xlink:href="qml-closeevent.xml">CloseEvent</db:link> contains an accepted property which can be set to false to abort closing the window.</db:para>
